briefdescription.para: I2CSlave driver implementation for the EUSCI controller on MSP432.

detaileddescription.para: This I2CSlave driver implementation is designed to operate on a EUCSI controller in I2CSlave mode. The I2CSlaveMSP432 header file should be included in an application as follows: #include<ti/drivers/I2CSlave.h> #include<ti/drivers/I2CSlaveMSP432.h>
